com.b2international.snowowl.emf.compare.diff.processor

Interface DiffProcessor<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of produced output.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiffProcessorImpl, LoggingDiffProcessor, NodeDeltaDiffProcessor, PrintStreamDiffProcessor, SnomedDiffProcessor, StringDiffProcessor

    public interface DiffProcessor<E>
    Difference processor representation. The processor is reposnsible to consume a difference and transform it any arbitrary object with a type of E.
